  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "jira-metrics-pg"
      },
      "description": "Hours since the last Jira sync attempt and its status. Green \u2264 12 h \u2022 Yellow 12\u201324 h \u2022 Red > 24 h or ERROR status. Queries most recent run regardless of success.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 12
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 24
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "h"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 2,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 999,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.1.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "jira-metrics-pg"
          },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (NOW() - finished_at)) / 3600.0, 1) AS \"Age (h)\",\n  UPPER(status) AS \"Status\"\nFROM sync_log\nWHERE finished_at IS NOT NULL\nORDER BY finished_at DESC LIMIT 1",
          "format": "table",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Data Age",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 2
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Jira Metrics\nKey engineering metrics across all teams and projects. Use the **Team / Project** filter to scope to your team. Use the links in the top-right to navigate to detailed dashboards."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Dashboards",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 2
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**[\ud83c\udfcb Sprint Health](/d/jira-sprint-health)**  \u2014 Velocity, delivery %, scope changes\n\n**[\ud83d\udc1b Quality & Bugs](/d/jira-quality-bugs)**  \u2014 Bug rates, priorities, releases\n\n**[\ud83d\udccb PO KPIs](/d/jira-po-kpis)**  \u2014 Planning accuracy, DOR/DOD, scope change\n\n**[\ud83c\udfb5 BOSE Workbench](/d/bose-workbench)**  \u2014 Bose epics & issues (WP- projects)\n\n---\n\n\ud83d\udcd6 **[Metrics Reference](https://github.com/Schpoe/jira-grafana-metrics/blob/master/docs/metrics-reference.md)**  \u2014 How every metric is calculated"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active Sprints",
      "description": "Number of sprints currently running across all selected teams.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "jira-metrics-pg"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "jira-metrics-pg"
          },
          "rawSql": "SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s.id) AS value FROM sprints s JOIN sprint_issues si ON si.sprint_id = s.id JOIN issues i ON i.key = si.issue_key WHERE s.state = 'active' AND i.project_key IN ($project)",
          "format": "table",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "fixed",
            "fixedColor": "blue"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Avg Delivery %",
      "description": "Story points delivered vs committed for the selected sprint.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 4,
        "y": 5
